<div class="text-bg">
<p class="title">Shi Ni Itaru Aka Volume 2 (JP)</p>
<p class="sub-title">Drag-on Dragoon 3</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="over-text-media">
<div class="text-bg">
<p class="title">Type</p>
<p class="sub-title">Manga</p>
<p class="title">Description</p>
<p class="sub-title">A manga following one of the branches of Drakengard 3, it follows a returning character and a new one: Nero.</p>
<p class="title">Where to find on THE HUMAN SERVER?</p>
<p class="sub-title">Access the reader service <u><a href="https://reader.thehumanserver.org/title?title=dod-3-snia-jp">here</a></u> for the JP scans, and <a href="/stories/drakengard-3/manga"><u>here</u></a> for the translated manga.</p>
</div>
</div>
